    "description": "We at Pugmarks India are looking for an experienced Reservation Manager based out of Bhopal. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Pugmarks India:\nPugmarks India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Pugmarks India!",
